      "fontSize": 11.086473269950128,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "LitePack ties Similarity on Faithfulness (1.000) and Answer Correctness (0.840) — matching the best on quality metrics.\nMMR is the only method with reduced faithfulness (0.980), suggesting its diversity penalty occasionally selects less\ngrounded content. LitePack achieves quality parity while also having best ROUGE-L (0.463) and lowest token count (1736).",
